overview: Elder Dudley’s journey into the all-male secret Mormon sex cult continues…Putting his trust in his priesthood leaders has been paying off, as Elder Dudley finds himself a few steps away from being ordained to the higher priesthood. But after having already received his second anointing, Elder Dudley gets caught fooling around with his handsome companion. The boy is disciplined and atones for his transgressions on the priesthood stretcher. Humbled, Elder Dudley enters into the covenant before finally being ordained to the true order of the higher priesthood!
title: Elder Dudley: Chapters 5-8
